# Frontend — Tailwind Rules

Use **Tailwind CSS** for styling.

- Prefer utility classes over custom CSS
- Avoid inline styles; use Tailwind classes
- Use design tokens (e.g. theme colors, spacing) from tailwind.config
- Keep responsive breakpoints consistent (sm, md, lg, xl)

Extract repeated class strings into components or constants when they grow long.
